 java.lang.String support 

In addition to the built-in methods, you can use standard methods of the java.lang.String class.



 java.lang.String.format() 

You can apply the standard Java String format() method to text. See [java.util.formatter reference](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/Formatter.htmlsyntax) for information about the syntax to use to specify the format details.

